sequenceDiagram
    participant Att as Attacker Foothold
    participant SA as Service A
    participant SB as Service B
    participant Policy as Policy + Identity Layer

    rect rgb(255,245,245)
    Note over Att,SB: Before mitigation
    Att->>SA: Compromise low-trust workload
    SA->>SB: Internal call (implicit trust)
    SB-->>SA: 200 allowed
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over Att,Policy: After mitigation
    Att->>SA: Compromise low-trust workload
    SA->>Policy: Present workload identity
    Policy-->>SA: Limited scope only
    SA->>SB: Attempt privileged call
    SB->>Policy: Verify caller identity + policy
    Policy-->>SB: deny
    SB-->>SA: 403 denied
    end
